This is a reference implementation of a runtime security gateway for
Model Context Protocol (MCP) tool calls. It is held to a documentation
honesty rule: every control claimed in the docs is matched to code and
a test, and the "Enforced today vs Roadmap" table in README.md is the
source of truth for what is actually enforced.
